{"type":"text","timestamp":1782443317254,"sessionID":"ses_0fe1aa5d9ffesFmHB6DHkAouwB","part":{"id":"prt_f01e68f39001U653xOi4i3NZsd","messageID":"msg_f01e665c1001faa5Qt14Giv9dm","sessionID":"ses_0fe1aa5d9ffesFmHB6DHkAouwB","type":"text","text":"I’m patching only the cart-group authority rows now. The target behavior is already present, so this is a narrow matrix repair with precise `implemented` vs `not-applicable` classifications, endpoints, and evidence tied to the cart route/store/tests.","time":{"start":1782443315001,"end":1782443317252}}}
