{"type":"text","timestamp":1782443713927,"sessionID":"ses_0fe1aa5d9ffesFmHB6DHkAouwB","part":{"id":"prt_f01ebfc1f001gDap7W89sxL2Rr","messageID":"msg_f01ebe35b0019CJ71ELOmk9pR8","sessionID":"ses_0fe1aa5d9ffesFmHB6DHkAouwB","type":"text","text":"Implemented the bounded cart-group repair. The target already had most cart behavior; I fixed one real cart UI parity gap and then updated only this group’s source-coverage authority rows with concrete endpoints and evidence.\n\nChanged files:\n- `Foodike-Harmony/entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/cart/cart_store.cj`: added local cart quantity mutation helpers so cart rows now update immediately like the source cart item card.\n- `Foodike-Harmony/entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/cart/cart_page.cj`: wired quantity controls into callbacks, kept note/coupon/delivery/bill route composition, and preserved veg/non-veg item badges.\n- `Foodike-Harmony/entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj`: added cart rerender state and hooked cart quantity callbacks into the cart route.\n- `Foodike-Harmony/entry/src/test/cangjie/phase05_detail_cart_state_mutations_test.cj`: added focused coverage for immediate local cart quantity mutation.\n- `translation-inputs/source-coverage-matrix.json`: closed the 17 cart-group rows with narrow `implemented` or `not-applicable` statuses, concrete target endpoints, and verification facts.\n- `translation-inputs/source-coverage-matrix.md`: markdown mirror synced by the authority patch tool.\n\nCovered current-phase gate entries:\n- `Cart.kt`\n  - `4c136b2d3d` navigation: closed as `implemented`\n  - `9969033ff2` lifecycle/entry initialization: closed as `implemented`\n  - `f1f520ab22` observable state propagation: closed as `implemented`\n  - `eaf4711dc9` image-viewing: closed as `not-applicable`\n  - `8c15fff266` runtime permission: closed as `not-applicable`\n- `CartViewModel.kt`\n  - `3db8c1ab5c` lifecycle/init: closed as `implemented`\n  