or checkout behavior, consistent with the source and phase plan.\n- False-positive rows for permissions/settings/image-viewer at the cart host, delivery card, coupon bar, and bill section were reclassified to `not-applicable` with source-backed notes.\n\nTests added or updated:\n- Updated `entry/src/test/cangjie/phase05_detail_cart_state_mutations_test.cj`\n- Added `Phase05DetailCartStateMutationsTest.cartStoreMutatesLocalQuantitiesImmediately`\n\nBuild result:\n- PASS after the cart fix using the Harmony build flow.\n- I did not attempt further test-harness repair beyond using the existing known blocker as evidence context.\n- The known test harness blocker remains:\n  - `translation-inputs/test-build-reports/phase-04-home-history-discovery/test-build-report.md`\n  - first blocker: `ld.lld: error: cannot open Scrt1.o: No such file or directory`\n\nCommands run:\n- `python .agents/skills/harmonyos-build/build.py --project-root \"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\Foodike-Harmony\"` twice\n- `C:\\Users\\Sieger\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python312\\python.exe D:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\scripts\\shared\\source_coverage\\patch_authority.py --kind matrix --authority \"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\source-coverage-matrix.json\" --patch \"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\tmp\\phase05-cart-matrix-patch.json\" --markdown \"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\source-coverage-matrix.md\" --plan-json \"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\plan.json\" --target-project \"D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\Foodike-Harmony\"`\n\nBuild result:\n- PASS: `translation-inputs/build-reports/phase-05-detail-cart-state-mutations/build-report.json`\n\nPlan changes:\n- none\n\nDeferred issues:\n- Test harness remains blocked outside this bounded cart-group repair:\n  - `phase-04-home-history-discovery` test report still fails at link time with missing `Scrt1.o` and related system libs.\n  - I used that as `harness-blocked` evidence where relevant instead of overstating test PASS.\n\nOut-of-scope whole-proj